"{\"uid\": \"usmagazine.com-entertainment-news-olympic-water-polo-star-cheered-on-by-husband-with-stage-4-cancer\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"OlympianMadeline Musselman, who plays water polo for Team USA, is being cheered on in her goal for athird gold medal in Parisby her husband - and nothing is going to stop him from supporting her.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17, \"end\": 26, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Musselman\", \"score\": 0.999999965691814, \"rank\": 3.430826376589135e-08, \"text\": \"Musselman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Musselman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Musselman\"}, {\"begin\": 53, \"end\": 61, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.7955413219963097, \"rank\": 0.20829981695751323, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Musselman, who is competing in her third Olympics and was named MVP for her team in Tokyo 2020, is married toPatrick Woepse, a fellow college water polo player who is currently battling a rare form of lung cancer.\", \"from\": 197, \"to\": 410, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 197, \"end\": 206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Musselman\", \"score\": 0.999999965691814, \"rank\": 3.430826376589135e-08, \"text\": \"Musselman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Musselman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Musselman\"}, {\"begin\": 261, \"end\": 264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Most_valuable_player\", \"score\": 0.9975959203729432, \"rank\": 0.002367206012987668, \"text\": \"MVP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Most_valuable_player\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Most_valuable_player\"}, {\"begin\": 281, \"end\": 286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9974295909976283, \"rank\": 0.0024256498769290704, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The couple, who both played their sport in college at UCLA, met in 2022 at a friend's wedding.\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 506, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 466, \"end\": 470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UCLA_Bruins\", \"score\": 0.9989564256511678, \"rank\": 0.000993896070455776, \"text\": \"UCLA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UCLA_Bruins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UCLA_Bruins\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A year later, they found themselves engaged, then struggling to make sense of a medical diagnosis that abruptly turned their lives upside down.\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 650, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a stage four lung cancer specific mutation,\\\" Woepse toldNBC Los Angelesin an interview published on TK, TKDATE.\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 769, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At that time I did not know what that meant.\\\"\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 816, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The two decided to marry as soon as possible, due to Woepse's uncertain life expectancy.\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 906, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All the people that came together to make it happen within four days - it was pretty crazy.\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 999, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We had flowers.\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We had a church that welcomed us with open arms to marry us.\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1076, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was just a perfect weekend,\\\" Musselman told the outlet.\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1135, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1109, \"end\": 1118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Musselman\", \"score\": 0.999999965691814, \"rank\": 3.430826376589135e-08, \"text\": \"Musselman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Musselman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Musselman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Woepse's diagnosis, however, did not stop him from cheering on his wife on her journey to Paris, even as he underwent chemotherapy treatments.\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1227, \"end\": 1232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999969345500777, \"rank\": 3.0654593487709165e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He encouraged her to go to practices, even when she wanted to be by his side during his health struggles.\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1385, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There are times where I wanted to be with him, but he's like, 'No, you have to go to practice,'\\\" Musselman said.\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1485, \"end\": 1494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Musselman\", \"score\": 0.999999965691814, \"rank\": 3.430826376589135e-08, \"text\": \"Musselman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Musselman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Musselman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Maddie Musselman Woepse (@maddiemusselman)    You have successfully subscribed.\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1521, \"end\": 1537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maddie_Musselman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maddie Musselman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maddie_Musselman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maddie_Musselman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By signing up, I agree to the Terms and Privacy Policy and to receive emails from Us Weekly  Check our latest news in Google News  Check our latest news in Apple News  Woepse not only urged Musselman to stick to her schedule, he even managed to make it to Paris so that he could see his wife and the U.S. women's water polo team beat Greece this week - cheering her on and ultimately celebrating with her in person.\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 2017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1758, \"end\": 1768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Apple News\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_News\"}, {\"begin\": 1792, \"end\": 1801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Musselman\", \"score\": 0.999999965691814, \"rank\": 3.430826376589135e-08, \"text\": \"Musselman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Musselman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Musselman\"}, {\"begin\": 1858, \"end\": 1863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999969345500777, \"rank\": 3.0654593487709165e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1936, \"end\": 1942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9608326056217487, \"rank\": 0.039988726266304314, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This was my biggest goal, with everything being so unknown,\\\" Woepse shared ofhis experience to NBC.\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2115, \"end\": 2118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.99250622327118, \"rank\": 0.005101409760947534, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So pretty emotional, emotional day for me.\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2163, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Could not be more thrilled to be here to support Maddie and the team.\\\"\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2234, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2213, \"end\": 2219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maddie_Coleman\", \"score\": 0.9998382012991086, \"rank\": 0.00016182488391205317, \"text\": \"Maddie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maddie_Coleman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maddie_Coleman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are sharing our story not for people to feel sorry for us or feel bad for what we are going through,\\\" Musselman explained of their unusual situation.\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2342, \"end\": 2351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Musselman\", \"score\": 0.999999965691814, \"rank\": 3.430826376589135e-08, \"text\": \"Musselman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Musselman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Musselman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If anything it's for inspiration and that you can get to the other side of things With the people that are right next to you, we hope for that.\\\"\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2535, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You have successfully subscribed.\", \"from\": 2537, \"